name: Matoi Ryuko (Kill La Kill)
description: Ryūko Matoi is the main protagonist in the Kill la Kill anime and manga. She is a nomadic transfer student who transfers to Honnōji Academy in search of the other half of a red Scissor Blade she carries, and the one who murdered her father, "Isshin Matoi" (real name: Sōichirō Kiryūin).
